# 🧩 SoftSell - Marketing Website

A modern, responsive, single-page marketing website built for a fictional software license resale startup called **SoftSell**. This project was created as part of a web development internship assignment with Credex.

---

## 🚀 Features Implemented

### ✅ Hero Section
- Headline and subheading introducing SoftSell
- Call-to-action button with smooth scroll to contact form

### ✅ How It Works
- Illustrated 3-step process:
  - Upload License
  - Get Valuation
  - Get Paid

### ✅ Why Choose Us
- 3 key selling points with icons:
  - Fast Process
  - Secure & Trusted
  - Excellent Support

### ✅ Customer Testimonials
- Two professionally styled dummy reviews to boost trust

### ✅ Contact / Lead Form
- Fields:
  - Name
  - Email
  - Company
  - License Type (dropdown)
  - Message
- Includes frontend validation
- Smooth and responsive design

---

## 🌙 Bonus Features

- 🎥 **Framer Motion Animations** on sections and buttons
- 🌗 **Dark / Light Mode Toggle**
- 🤖 **Mock AI Chat Assistant** (`ChatWidget.jsx`) for basic interaction
- 🌐 SEO-friendly structure with clean headings and metadata
- ⚡ Smooth scroll behavior from CTA to contact form

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React.js with Vite
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Deployment Ready**: Easily host on Vercel, Netlify, or GitHub Pages

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

SoftSell-Marketing-Site/
